==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Angelize
<hw>An"gel*ize</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To raise to
the state of an angel; to render angelic.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>It ought not to be our object to <qex>angelize</qex>, nor to
brutalize, but to humanize man.</q> <rj><qau>W. Taylor.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Angellike</ent>⟦br⟧
